----------------------------------------------------------------------

Kitchen Fleva: Environment Configuration Examples (.env.example)

----------------------------------------------------------------------

--- 1. SUPABASE CONFIGURATION (MANDATORY) -----------------------------

These keys are required for the Supabase JavaScript Client connection.

The URL and ANON_KEY are public and can be safely used on the client-side.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://your-project-id.supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="your-public-anon-key-that-starts-with-eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."

The SERVICE_ROLE_KEY MUST NOT be exposed to the client. Used by secure Supabase Edge Functions.

SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="your-private-service-role-key-that-starts-with-eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET="your-jwt-secret-for-signing-custom-tokens"

--- 2. AI INTEGRATION (GEMINI API) -----------------------------------

Used by Supabase Edge Functions for recipe/blog/video generation.

GEMINI_API_KEY="your-gemini-api-key"

Model for general text tasks (recipe instructions, blog writing)

AI_TEXT_MODEL="gemini-2.5-flash-preview-09-2025"

Model for image generation tasks (imageEnhancer)

AI_IMAGE_MODEL="imagen-3.0-generate-002"

--- 3. PAYMENT GATEWAYS (M-PESA, STRIPE, PAYPAL, etc.) ---------------

These keys are highly sensitive and MUST only be used inside Supabase Edge Functions.

M-PESA (Safaricom, Kenya)

MPESA_CONSUMER_KEY="your-mpesa-consumer-key"
MPESA_CONSUMER_SECRET="your-mpesa-consumer-secret"
MPESA_LIPA_NA_PASSKEY="your-mpesa-lipa-na-mpesa-online-passkey"
MPESA_SHORTCODE="your-business-shortcode"
MPESA_CALLBACK_URL="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://your-project-id.supabase.co/functions/v1/payment-webhook"

STRIPE

STRIPE_SECRET_KEY="sk_live_..."
STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY="pk_live_..." # This one can be exposed to the client (used by checkout.js)
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET="whsec_..."

PAYPAL

PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID="your-paypal-client-id" # Can be exposed for client-side buttons
PAYPAL_SECRET="your-paypal-secret"

FLUTTERWAVE

FLUTTERWAVE_PUBLIC_KEY="FW_PUBK_..." # Can be exposed to the client
FLUTTERWAVE_SECRET_KEY="FW_SECK_..."

PAYSTACK

PAYSTACK_PUBLIC_KEY="pk_live_..." # Can be exposed to the client
PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY="sk_live_..."

--- 4. EMAIL SERVICE -------------------------------------------------

Used by the sendEmail Supabase Edge Function (e.g., SendGrid, Resend, or SMTP)

EMAIL_SERVICE_API_KEY="your-email-service-api-key"
EMAIL_SENDER_ADDRESS="noreply@kitchenfleva.com"

--- 5. ANALYTICS & MONITORING ----------------------------------------

For external logging or analytics services (e.g., Google Analytics ID)

VITE_GA_TRACKING_ID="UA-XXXXXXX-Y"

----------------------------------------------------------------------

Remember: NEVER commit sensitive keys to GitHub.

Use a separate, private .env file in development.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
